Subject: Networking for Awkward People
Description: Ever find yourself at a networking event, unable to think of how to introduce yourself to the people around you? As sweat pours down your face, do you say, 'Hi, my name is Annalisa,' and then just blank? We've got you covered. You'll walk out with a full-proof 'elevator pitch' and tactics to conquer any nerves, small talk or curveballs. Be warned - you'll actually be up and moving and trying this out on your fellow attendees. And make eye contact.  Speakers include:Chioke Mose-Telesford, Jennifer Cline - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
